//@10344    = ~Woodland Cloak~
@10345    = ~The leaves that fall from the great oak of Kuldahar are surprisingly flexible, much like cloth, and when treated with special druidic magics, can be fashioned as cloaks. When worn, the cloaks make no sound, and they provide the wearer with a minor chameleon effect, allowing them to blend into the natural surroundings and avoid the notice of those that would do the wearer harm. Furthermore, in times of danger, the wearer may wrap the cloak around their body, making their skin as hard as wood and helping to protect them against attack.

STATISTICS:

