@10372    = ~Worn by wizards and scholars across Faerun, the distinctive small, round school caps come in a variety of colors. The colors often correspond to scholastic colors or the color associated with a particular school of magic. This particular cap was worn by the wizard Vedri of Silverymoon. On a sightseeing tour of Icewind Dale, his skiff capsized on Maer Dualdon. Fishermen later recovered his body. They sold the cap as compensation for sending his body back to his family.

