Max Dex Bonus:  +5
Armor Check Penalty:  -1
Arcane Spell Failure:  15%
Special:
  Wearer is under the effect of Nondetection.
  Move Silently skill: +6
  The armor bonus of Interloper is increased by 1 for every 5 points of Move Silently the wearer has.
Weight: 5 lb.~
