@10587    = ~Celestial Aura~
@10588    = ~Aasimars are direct offspring from a union between mortal and celestial minion. While normally carrying innate powers, it is not unusual for an Aasimar to don blessed armor. Such is the case for this unique armor known as Celestial Aura. The armor shimmers with a silvery glow and is adorned with exquisite blue etchings across the breast. One look at the armor and it is simple to see that it possesses powerful protections. 

