@10652    = ~This red iron tower shield reaches nearly from the chin to the toe of the user. It is heavy even for a shield of its size, much of the weight coming from a large sculpted dragon's head set into its face - the head, wrought in the same red metal as the rest of the shield, protrudes almost like a gargoyle from a castle wall.

