//@10761    = ~Xvimian Fang~
@10762    = ~As gratitude and a show of good faith towards Saablic Tan for joining with the Legion of the Chimera, Isair and Madae gave Saablic the Xvimian Fang dagger.

Forged from the finest metals and enchanted with the darkest magics akin to Xvimian lore, the Xvimian Fang reflects no light from its blackened steel. The blade is so black, in fact, that any details that usually stand out from a curved dagger blade are completely absent. It is as if the blade actually absorbs light. 

Saablic Tan always keeps the Xvimian Fang close, not just because the dagger has the awesome power to potentially turn individuals to stone, but because the dagger increased the potency of his acid spells - truly a powerful weapon befitting a powerful wizard.

