@11430    = ~An azure rod is not a unique item, but certainly a rare one. Each is fashioned from a durable silvery-white alloy and capped with a large, softly glowing sphere of lapis lazuli. Intricate designs wind their way around the azure rod's shaft and head, but none serve to indicate who or what might have had a hand in their creation.

