//@12063    = ~Mossy Poultice~
@12064    = ~The druids of the Moonshae Isles carried these small urns with them as they walked with the war bands of the Moonshae. The urns were reported to carry moss that had grown on the field of battle, and when the poultice was applied to the wounds of warriors and adventurers, it aided their recovery. 

