@12092    = ~This thick liquid is harvested and distilled from the glands of dead polar worms. It is the substance that helps keep the huge creatures warm in the desolate north. Drinking the liquid straight from the creature's body is almost always fatal, so alchemists attempt to distill the substance until it is relatively safe to consume. Even in its current state, however, it can still be deadly.

