//@12207    = ~Book of Leaves~ //HoF
@12208    = ~The covers of this heavy book are made of bark, and the pages are made of pressed leaves. It is not clear what is holding this book together, for you see no bindings and no glue along the spine.

When this book is held in the hand of a druid and the druid is touching solid ground, a sheath of bark will sprout from the earth and cover the wielder, making his skin as tough as the skin of a great tree. 
 
